{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9cde12993c","title":"中央转发山东分局关于城市镇反经验报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ed1209b971","index":0,"year":1951,"month":4,"day":7,"articleId":"9cde12993c"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ab6519beac","type":"title","text":"中央转发山东分局关于城市镇反经验报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cde12993c"},{"id":"cc30534bc9","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cde12993c"},{"id":"fadf19cb2e","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局，并转分局，省委，区党委，大中市委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cde12993c"},{"id":"5753f82334","type":"paragraph","text":"城市镇反工作，山东有一个很好的经验，华东局已给批准并转发华东各地参考。请你们也参考此项经验，正确地展开城市的镇反工作。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cde12993c"},{"id":"edbcf99888","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央四月七日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cde12993c"}],"page":{"id":"dc2911af1e","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"9cde12993c","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"ad249d758b","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"9cde12993c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央山东分局、山东省公安厅1951年4月3日关于全省统一行动速捕反革命的经验报告。他们的做法是：（一）召开全省公安、司法、检察会议，统一部署，订出行动计划。（二）对材料的搜集与审查，事先均经城乡交流，互相查对，保证不错捕一人。（三）进行思想与奥论的动员。（四）以市公安局为主，结合驻军，组织行动指挥部，并对所有人员进行政策、业务、保密等的教育训练，制定行动守则，颁布纪律。（五）吸收民主人士参加城乡联络委员会，参与对某些人犯材料证据的审查。（六）为保证此次行动不发生内部意外事件，在行动前，将警察中的坏分子先行清洗和关押一批，将潜伏在工厂企业内部的罪证确、有现实危害可能的反革命分子先抓了一批。"}],"contents":[{"id":"11028d4679","type":"paragraph","text":"四月七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"9cde12993c"},{"id":"7844c33e24","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"9cde12993c"},{"id":"97b04b026e","type":"paragraph","text":"城市镇反工作，山东有一个很好的经验“，华东局已给批准并转发华东各地参考。请你们也参考此项经验，正确地展开城市的镇反工作。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"9cde12993c"},{"id":"990c6fb51f","type":"title","text":"中央转发山东分局关于城市镇反经验报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"9cde12993c"},{"id":"ad249d758b","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，并转分局，省委，区党委，大中市委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"9cde12993c"}],"page":{"id":"d293a365b1","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"9cde12993c","start":222,"end":222}}}},"__N_SSG":true}